# task #134 (Reconnect): a fresh daemon that DIES must produce the honest failure token
# (not-running) with the why captured in the ts log (exit rc + the daemon's own words) —
# never a fake "Reconnected".
desc tailscale-lib: Reconnect whose fresh daemon dies -> not-running, why captured
invoke tslib
tsdaemon die
sdfile+ .userdata/tg5040/tailscale/tailscaled.state
tsdrv reconnect
expect_exit 0
expect_trace TSDRV reconnect rc=1 tok=not-running
expect_file_has .userdata/tg5040/tailscale/tailscaled.log tailscaled EXITED (rc=1) before its socket appeared
expect_file_has .userdata/tg5040/tailscale/tailscaled.log reconnect: restart did not reach Running
